  "htmlMain": "<div id=\"pl-3157\" class=\"panel-layout\"><div id=\"pg-3157-0\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-3157-0-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3157-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://buy.stripe.com/9B66oId7OgH824N2Dn8so0k\">Help Support Our Mural</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mural Activity/Coloring Book $9.99/each (shipping charges additional TBA)</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">To get your books please contact our office: info@RaleighHillsBusinessAssn.org</p>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-3904 aligncenter\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578-226x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578-226x300.jpg 226w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578-100x133.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578-150x199.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578-200x266.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578-300x398.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578-450x598.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578-280x372.jpg 280w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/IMG_3578.jpg 482w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 226px) 100vw, 226px\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3868 aligncenter\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof-281x300.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof-281x300.png 281w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof-100x107.png 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof-150x160.png 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof-200x214.png 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof-300x321.png 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof-450x481.png 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof-280x299.png 280w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/coaster-proof.png 567w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 217px) 100vw, 217px\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Stairway mural photo-shopped to get a full visual effect.</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3411 aligncenter\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/stairs-27-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/stairs-27-200x300.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/stairs-27-100x150.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/stairs-27-150x225.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/stairs-27.jpg 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><strong><em>About the Mural: </em></strong>It started as a conversation with two businesses in Raleigh Hills who were concerned about tagging and vandalism. As the managers of Raleigh Hills Fred Meyer and Courtyard Village researched anti-graffiti protective covering, an idea for producing a public art project was born. Thanks to generous funding from Venture Portland, Explore Tualatin Valley and support from the Raleigh Hills Business Association, the Mural on The Stairs project began.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3558 alignleft\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-300x147.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-300x147.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-100x49.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-150x73.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-200x98.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-450x220.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-600x294.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo.jpg 725w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 181px) 100vw, 181px\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3455 alignleft\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679-300x232.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679-300x232.png 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679-768x593.png 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679-100x77.png 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679-150x116.png 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679-200x155.png 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679-450x348.png 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679-600x464.png 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Stacked_Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_Forest_Green_WEB-1747877679.png 792w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 132px) 100vw, 132px\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3450 alignleft\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Color-masthead-300x194.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n\n\n<p>The active senior living community at Courtyard Village helped shape this project by providing invaluable feedback. They participated in surveys and discussions with our local historian Carolyn Woods. We felt that their inclusion and the connection and engagement with them emulated the tradition of respect for elders in the native culture.&nbsp;<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-3451 aligncenter\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/court-yard-village-logo-300x97.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/court-yard-village-logo-300x97.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/court-yard-village-logo-100x32.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/court-yard-village-logo-150x49.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/court-yard-village-logo-200x65.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/court-yard-village-logo-450x146.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/court-yard-village-logo-600x195.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/court-yard-village-logo.jpg 622w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 173px) 100vw, 173px\"></p>\n<p>Our muralist, Stacy Lynn Smith, worked to tie in all the elements that were important to celebrate and appreciate here and now in Raleigh Hills. The Gorge was the lifeline for commerce, hunting, fishing and transportation. The outside wall pays homage to the Columbia Gorge. Special thanks to Bob Hansen for the beautiful text work that he contributed. The inside walls of the stairs celebrate the salmon, the wildlife and native plants that existed when the “first peoples” walked here, lived here and had their families here. It is their footsteps we honor. When people walk up or down the stairs they are embraced &nbsp;by the peace of the landscape as it was in those days</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3732 aligncenter\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-300x232.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-300x232.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-1024x791.jpg 1024w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-768x593.jpg 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-1536x1187.jpg 1536w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-2048x1583.jpg 2048w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-100x77.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-150x116.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-200x155.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-450x348.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-600x464.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-900x695.jpg 900w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Mural-Map-Final-280x216.jpg 280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px\"></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">To view the mural, please park in the RH Fred Meyer parking lot, off SW 77th Avenue.&nbsp; There is no public parking at Courtyard Village.</h4>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;Info contact RHBA: <a href=\"info@RaleighHillsBusinessAssn.org\">info@RaleighHillsBusinessAssn.org</a></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/mural\"><em>https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/mural</em></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3558 aligncenter\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-300x147.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-300x147.jpg 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-100x49.jpg 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-150x73.jpg 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-200x98.jpg 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-450x220.jpg 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo-600x294.jpg 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Venture-Portland-logo.jpg 725w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 168px) 100vw, 168px\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-3452 aligncenter\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611-300x46.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611-300x46.png 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611-768x118.png 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611-100x15.png 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611-150x23.png 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611-200x31.png 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611-450x69.png 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611-600x92.png 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Explore_Tualatin_Valley_Logo_Pinot_WEB-e1702332027578-3866435611.png 792w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 274px) 100vw, 274px\">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</p>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-3157-1\" class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"><div id=\"pgc-3157-1-0\" class=\"panel-grid-cell\"><div id=\"panel-3157-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\"><div class=\"textwidget\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The RHBA Mural Team Collaborated with the Muralists: Stacy Lynn Smith&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.stacylynnsmith.com/\">https://www.stacylynnsmith.com/ </a>and Bob Hansen <a href=\"https://www.inknife.co/\">https://www.inknife.co/</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-3737\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-300x46.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-300x46.png 300w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-768x118.png 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-100x15.png 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-150x23.png 150w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-200x31.png 200w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-450x69.png 450w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-600x92.png 600w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos-280x43.png 280w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mural-sponsors-montage-of-logos.png 807w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 561px) 100vw, 561px\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>RHBA received 2 Grants; 1 </strong><strong>from Venture Portland&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ventureportland.org/\">https://venturepo</a></strong><strong><a href=\"https://ventureportland.org/\">rtland.org/</a> and the 2nd from Explore Tualatin Valley&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tualatinvalley.org/\">https://tualatinvalley.org/</a>.<br>\n</strong></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3734\" src=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/VP-report-Competed-262x300.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/VP-report-Competed-262x300.png 262w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/VP-report-Competed-768x879.png 768w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/VP-report-Competed-100x114.png 100w, https://raleighhillsbusinessassn.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/VP-report-Competed-150